  <brief_title>Efficacy of TAK-438 Compared to AG-1749 (Lansoprazole) in the Treatment of Erosive Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-Blind, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of TAK-438 (20 mg Once-Daily) Compared to AG-1749 (30mg Once-Daily) in Patients With Erosive Esophagitis</official_title>
