  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the efficacy of TAK-438, once daily (QD), compared
      to lansoprazole in patients with erosive esophagitis of Grade A to D as defined by the LA
      classification grading system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
